---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
// We no longer need to import a logo component, so that line is removed.
---

<Layout title="Singular: Own Less. Control More.">
	<div class="text-center">
		<div class="mb-12 flex flex-col items-center">
			<img src="/logo.png" alt="Singular Protocol Logo" class="w-48 h-48 mb-6" />
			
			<h1 class="text-5xl font-bold mb-4">Own Less. Control More.</h1>
			<p class="text-xl text-gray-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
				Singular is a decentralized investment protocol governed by its community, with a token whose value is backed by a portfolio of real assets.
			</p>
		</div>

		<div class="mb-16">
			<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">A New Economic Primitive</h2>
			<p class="text-lg max-w-3xl mx-auto">
				Traditional tokenomics leads to high supply and value dilution. Singular pioneers a new model anchored in absolute scarcity and intrinsic value, where the success of the protocol directly translates to the value of the token.
			</p>
		</div>
		
		<div class="mb-16">
			<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8">A Self-Sustaining Economic Engine</h2>
			<div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
				<div class="p-6 border border-gray-700 rounded-lg">
					<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Capital Allocation</h3>
					<p>The DAO deploys capital from its treasury into promising new ventures via a formal, community-led proposal and voting process.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="p-6 border border-gray-700 rounded-lg">
					<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Intrinsic Value Growth</h3>
					<p>The value of the SNG token is intrinsically linked to the Net Asset Value (NAV) of the treasury's investment portfolio.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="p-6 border border-gray-700 rounded-lg">
					<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Profit-Sharing Dividends</h3>
					<p>Profits from successful investments are returned to token holders as dividends, rewarding long-term commitment and effective governance.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div>
			<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Explore the Full Vision</h2>
			<p class="text-lg mb-6">
				Our whitepaper provides a complete overview of the Singular protocol, including our detailed tokenomics, governance model, security commitments, and roadmap.
			</p>
			<p>
				<a href="[YOUR_WHITEPAPER_PDF_LINK]" class="btn btn-lg sm:min-w-64">Read the Whitepaper</a>
			</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</Layout>